contract.name: BaseDAsa
contract.desc:
Base D-ASA Class implementing common interfaces and state schema:

    - Asset creation and configuration
    - Role-based access control
    - Account management (creation, suspension, close-out)
    - Primary distribution
    - Getters (asset info, account info, time events)

args.name: minimum_denomination
args.desc: Minimum denomination, expressed in denomination asset

args.name: time_periods
args.desc: Time periods of recurring time events

methods.desc: Configure the Debt Algorand Standard Asset

args.name: secondary_market_time_events
args.desc: Secondary market time events (strictly ascending order)

returns.desc: Secondary Market Opening Date, Secondary Market Closure Date

methods.desc: Assign a role to an address

methods.name: revoke_role
methods.desc: Revoke a role from an address

args.desc: Amount of D-ASA units to distribute
